This is a simple chatbot built using Flask for the user interface and Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to enrich responses with relevant text. The added content is transformed into embeddings, enabling the chatbot to answer questions based on the defined dataset.

The dependent packages are defined in requirements.txt.

1.	Clone the repo - https://github.com/neerajp12345/myrepo
2.	Created virtual env “Python -m venv .venv”, followed by activating it
3.	Install: pip install -r requirements.txt
4.	Run: python chatbot.py

* Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000
Press CTRL+C to quit
 * Restarting with stat
Starting RAG WebApp with Gemini...

